{"tid":1180253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★華為死機：事件屬於個別手機更新問題","createTime":"2019-05-31T16:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T09:53:29.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7cd071f78d4780a3857d3e75e1c2b983933b0e8c","tid":1180253,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"華為手機系統更新檔出問題，有香港用家前日(29日)更新後驚見「死機」，手機無法正常啟動，不少人到華為位於旺角的客戶服務中心了解及維修。華為表示，經調查後，發現<span style=\"color: red;\">事件屬於個別手機更新問題</span>，並對受影響的用家深表歉意。<br />\n<br />\n華為指，有關問題已得到修正，技術人員已陸續為受影響顧客解決了手機異常情況，預計今日(31日)或之前完成受影響手機的修復。華為建議，顧客近日凡遇到關於手機更新的問題，可致電或前往客戶服務中心，相關人員會按步驟指導用家進行更新。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190531/bkn-20190531231317497-0531_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190531%2Fbkn-20190531231317497-0531_00822_001.html&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=d7ca0b34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190531/bkn-20190531231317497-0531_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2477c44229c9db657e7938dd169aa54fe25e1d89","tid":1180253,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:38:10.000Z","msg":"個別問題"},{"pid":"c5ca77f45fbfc40f960be4b1640ae0930168e876","tid":1180253,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"全部人既個別問題"},{"pid":"c4890b0590c10f268f92205f33a158904d3f16a0","tid":1180253,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:38:31.000Z","msg":"用家問題"},{"pid":"c54bb09a1143eff3ceea804471886c8e081d6ed6","tid":1180253,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5ca77f45fbfc40f960be4b1640ae0930168e876","tid":1180253,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"全部人既個別問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:39:02.000Z","msg":"香港問題<br />\n<br />\n佔中問題"},{"pid":"569d8997a69327094